The '''Nightsister Stronghold''' was located on [[Dathomir/Legends|Dathomir]], the [[Homeworld/Legends|homeworld]] of the [[Nightsisters/Legends|Nightsisters]]. It served as a refugee settlement for the exiled witches.

Right outside the walls of the stronghold was the entrance to the [[Rancor Cave]], where many [[Rancor/Legends|rancors]] lived.<ref name="SWG:RC">{{SWGcite|exp=AED|type=poi|Rancor Cave|Dathomir}}</ref> The entrance to the [[Chamber of Banishment]] could be found in the deepest part of the caverns.<ref name="SWG:AM">{{SWGcite|exp=NGE|type=heroic|Axkva Min}}</ref>
